text: John Thomas Higgins (1874–1916) was an English footballer who played in the Football League for West Bromwich Albion with whom he played in the 1895 FA Cup Final. ==References== Category:1874 births Category:1916 deaths Category:English footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Stourbridge F.C. players Category:West Bromwich Albion F.C. players Category:English Football League players Category:Date of birth missing Category:Date of death missing
